{"TopicId":187315,"ForumId":148,"TopicTitle":"Kerbal Space Program 2: Master Post","CreatedByName":"sh1pman","CreatedById":147869,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-19T23:28:00Z","PageNum":35,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"AHHans","CreatedById":197939,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-22T11:43:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223656608\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187315\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221566472922\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002257455\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Paul Kingtiger\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n10 minutes ago, Paul Kingtiger said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI don\u0027t know.\u00A0 I would assume that the percentages are roughly the same.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGiven how KSP resonates with the geeky mindset I don\u0027t believe that there aren\u0027t relatively more Linux users in the KSP userbase than in the general Steam userbase.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt would be O.K. (not great, but O.K.) for me if it was a purely economic decision. But I\u0027m afraid that there is also a certain level of \u0022mental laziness\u0022 involved (in particular with the big companies). \u0022We did it like this all the time, why change it.\u0022 \u0022If it is fine for Borderlands 42, why do it differently for KSP 2?\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"KSK","CreatedById":61025,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-22T11:52:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223656560\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187315\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221566466892\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002273725\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u00225thHorseman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, 5thHorseman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNobody\u0027s talking about the really big story, here.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn KSP2 the sun will officially be named Kerbol.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat\u0027s enough for me to want to not buy it right there.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNo problem - add a Sun/Kerbol toggle in the game settings. It could go right under the \u2018level of micro transactions\u2019 slider and the \u2018clear all mods\u2019 button. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022;)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"fulgur","CreatedById":195204,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-22T12:10:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAll OSes are equal, but Linux OSes are more equal than others. - Not George Orwell, Animal Farm.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf KSP2 does not go on Linux I don\u0027t want to buy it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"JAFO","CreatedById":132901,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-22T12:45:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223656560\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187315\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221566466892\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002273725\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u00225thHorseman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, 5thHorseman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNobody\u0027s talking about the really big story, here.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn KSP2 the sun will officially be named Kerbol.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat\u0027s enough for me to want to not buy it right there.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nComing from someone who has recently made comments to others to the effect of not getting stressed out over minor irrelevancies, that\u0027s kind of...\u00A0 amusing.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd it\u0027s not like it (presumably) can\u0027t very easily be modded to whatever you prefer.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MechBFP","CreatedById":184845,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-22T13:06:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223656660\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187315\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221566477944\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022132901\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022JAFO\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n20 minutes ago, JAFO said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nComing from someone who has recently made comments to others to the effect of not getting stressed out over minor irrelevancies, that\u0027s kind of...\u00A0 amusing.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd it\u0027s not like it (presumably) can\u0027t very easily be modded to whatever you prefer.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI believe that post was sarcasm, lol.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"JERONIMO","CreatedById":188491,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-22T13:09:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAt least add the kraken button\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DunaManiac","CreatedById":176003,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-22T14:08:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI believe that KSP2 could evolve into 2 kinds of games\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E1: A glorified version of KSP\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E2: An entirely new game similar to KSP\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003EI don\u0027t want KSP2 to just be a glorified version of KSP1 because what is the point in buying it?\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003EWhat I would like in KSP2 is something that retains the same spirit of KSP1, but is different enough\u00A0 so that is worth buying\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u00A0\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E(But still can\u0027t wait until KSP2 launches!\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E)\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u00A0\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Superfluous J","CreatedById":73725,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-22T14:38:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223656660\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187315\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221566477944\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022132901\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022JAFO\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, JAFO said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nComing from someone who has recently made comments to others to the effect of not getting stressed out over minor irrelevancies, that\u0027s kind of...\u00A0 amusing.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd it\u0027s not like it (presumably) can\u0027t very easily be modded to whatever you prefer.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell my tongue is planted quite firmly in my cheek there. It won\u0027t actually keep me from buying the game.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso, it\u0027s a fact I garnered from several sources of official information about the game, as opposed to random speculation.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"sprite8008","CreatedById":199666,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-22T15:07:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\ni hope you tell me about colonialization that mentioned during interview\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ni couldnt understand without subtitles because im not good at listening\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Technical Ben","CreatedById":10512,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-22T15:12:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223656560\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187315\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221566466892\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002273725\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u00225thHorseman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 hours ago, 5thHorseman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNobody\u0027s talking about the really big story, here.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn KSP2 the sun will officially be named Kerbol.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat\u0027s enough for me to want to not buy it right there.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs this a joke? \u003Cimg alt=\u0022;)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s gonna have multiple star systems... actually... well, in my Sci-Fi I\u0027d have people in space rename the \u0022sun\u0022 to \u0022sol\u0022 to avoid confusion when orbiting \u0022a *sun*\u0022. But people on Earth would just call it \u0022the sun\u0022 because they\u0027d not be looking at stella maps unless working at \u0022stellar maps R us Co\u0022. \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Greenfire32","CreatedById":36705,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-22T15:51:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSomething I haven\u0027t seen much info on: does KSP2 come packaged with all the content that\u0027s in both DLCs for KSP1?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBecause I\u0027ve become accustomed to having certain parts from both and it would be a \u00222 steps forward, 1 step back\u0022 kind of scenario if KSP2 didn\u0027t come with everything KSP1 has to offer plus new stuff exclusive to KSP2.\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nAs of right now, I\u0027m operating under the assumption that KSP2 is the entirety of KSP1 with all the fancy new colonization, interstellar stuff, and maybe a graphical and mechanical overhaul added in.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"That John","CreatedById":195544,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-22T16:24:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nthe trailer literally makes me cry.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nalso, will polish language be supported in ksp 2?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"VoidCosmos","CreatedById":192336,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-22T16:41:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223656825\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187315\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221566491060\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022195544\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022That John\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n17 minutes ago, That John said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nthe trailer literally makes me cry.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nalso, will polish language be supported in ksp 2?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMaybe........\n\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223656795\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187315\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221566489065\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002236705\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Greenfire32\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n50 minutes ago, Greenfire32 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSomething I haven\u0027t seen much info on: does KSP2 come packaged with all the content that\u0027s in both DLCs for KSP1?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBecause I\u0027ve become accustomed to having certain parts from both and it would be a \u00222 steps forward, 1 step back\u0022 kind of scenario if KSP2 didn\u0027t come with everything KSP1 has to offer plus new stuff exclusive to KSP2.\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nAs of right now, I\u0027m operating under the assumption that KSP2 is the entirety of KSP1 with all the fancy new colonization, interstellar stuff, and maybe a graphical and mechanical overhaul added in.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt may be like this:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n1: The docs may be merged with the game\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n2: It\u0027s SQUAD\u0027s idea\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Wolframmington","CreatedById":199570,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-22T18:56:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCannot wait!\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022105.88\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022 width=\u002217\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022105.88\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022 width=\u002217\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022105.88\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022 width=\u002217\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Ratwerke_Actual","CreatedById":189744,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-22T19:24:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223656360\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187315\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221566444815\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022196529\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022The Doodling Astronaut\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n15 hours ago, The Doodling Astronaut said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHere is an official quote from KSP twitter. It is getting tiring to keep hearing if there will be micro-transactions\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u