3C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRead the intent, not the words. The people writing that aren\u2019t lawyers, so stop analyzing it like they are. \u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-08-22T21:36:33Z\u0022 title=\u002208/22/2019 09:36  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003EAugust 22, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by MechBFP\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kerbart","CreatedById":78303,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-22T21:41:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223657105\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187315\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221566509769\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022184845\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022MechBFP\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 minutes ago, MechBFP said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRead the intent, not the words. The people writing that aren\u2019t lawyers, so stop analyzing it like they are. \u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThey haven\u2019t denied that it\u2019s going the be a first-person shooter game either, so we\u2019re forced to assume that\u2019s what it\u2019s going to be, right?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u2019m glad someone brought up the micro-transactions though, it\u2019s about time!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"hello there","CreatedById":184102,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-22T21:43:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223657110\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187315\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221566510066\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002278303\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Kerbart\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, Kerbart said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThey haven\u2019t denied that it\u2019s going the be a first-person shooter game either\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nreally? go to\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.kerbalspaceprogram.com/game/kerbal-space-program-2/\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://www.kerbalspaceprogram.com/game/kerbal-space-program-2/\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0first\u00A0paragraph\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Pthigrivi","CreatedById":105624,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-22T21:47:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHey btw is this forum the official venue for feedback and conversation about\u00A0about KSP2? They mentioned how much they appreciated the community built up around KSP1 but I haven\u0027t seen anyone from Star Theory chime in here, just the Squad folks.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-08-22T21:48:23Z\u0022 title=\u002208/22/2019 09:48  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003EAugust 22, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by Pthigrivi\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"SilverlightPony","CreatedById":79637,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-22T21:51:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223657116\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187315\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221566510469\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022105624\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Pthigrivi\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, Pthigrivi said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHey btw is this forum the official venue for feedback and conversation about\u00A0about KSP2? They mentioned how much they appreciated the community built up around KSP1 but I haven\u0027t seen anyone from Star Theory chime in here, just the Squad folks.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe SQUAD folks posting in here may not be part of the Star.Theory dev team, but their job (particularly those with the title \u0022community manager\u0022 or something along those lines) is specifically to stay in touch with us, and they definitely have some level of communication with the Star.Theory guys.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"razark","CreatedById":32993,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-22T21:51:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223657112\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187315\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221566510231\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022184102\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022hello there\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 minutes ago, hello there said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nreally? go to\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.kerbalspaceprogram.com/game/kerbal-space-program-2/\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://www.kerbalspaceprogram.com/game/kerbal-space-program-2/\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0first\u00A0paragraph\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI don\u0027t see anything there saying that it won\u0027t be a FPS.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPersonally, I think we should all just panic over what might happen, and throw out useless speculation regarding what will or won\u0027t be in the game, multiplayer, microtransactions, DLC, bugs, and everything else.\u00A0 That way, we\u0027ll have something to do while we wait for any \u003Cstrong\u003Eactual\u003C/strong\u003E information to get worked up over.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Pthigrivi","CreatedById":105624,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-22T22:01:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223657120\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187315\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221566510681\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002279637\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022SilverlightPony\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 minutes ago, SilverlightPony said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe SQUAD folks posting in here may not be part of the Star.Theory dev team, but their job (particularly those with the title \u0022community manager\u0022 or something along those lines) is specifically to stay in touch with us, and they definitely have some level of communication with the Star.Theory guys.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCool. Didn\u0027t know if there was a plan in place to make a new official forum or if this one would serve both projects going forward. I actually quite agree Squad has been super receptive to community feedback and I hope that continues with KSP2.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Superfluous J","CreatedById":73725,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-22T22:09:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223656766\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187315\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221566486759\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002210512\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Technical Ben\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n10 hours ago, Technical Ben said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs this a joke? \u003Cimg alt=\u0022;)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022105.88\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022 width=\u002217\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s gonna have multiple star systems... actually... well, in my Sci-Fi I\u0027d have people in space rename the \u0022sun\u0022 to \u0022sol\u0022 to avoid confusion when orbiting \u0022a *sun*\u0022. But people on Earth would just call it \u0022the sun\u0022 because they\u0027d not be looking at stella maps unless working at \u0022stellar maps R us Co\u0022. \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022105.88\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022 width=\u002217\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt could be called Sun. Or S\u00FCn. Or Suhn. Or Johnny. My problem isn\u0027t that it has a name. My problem is that the name is Kerbol. It\u0027s like fingernails on a chalkboard to my brain.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-08-23T01:48:59Z\u0022 title=\u002208/23/2019 01:48  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003EAugust 23, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by 5thHorseman\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Chel","CreatedById":176173,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-22T22:17:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223656605\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187315\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221566472647\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022199637\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022CursedLight\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n10 hours ago, CursedLight said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGiven the little gameplay footage in the IGN video, extra launch sites are in the base game.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWas talking about the KSP DLC, not the KSP 2 trailer\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}